SAP SD Consultant
SAP SD Consultant
Location:  Singapore
Senior SAP SD Consultant- Permanent- Singapore
Job Responsibilities:
•	Role of internal consultant within projects
•	Implement, test and document the customized business processes
•	Realization of reports, queries, etc.
•	Provide 2nd level support to key users (Incident management)
•	Problem and change owner
•	Role of consultant within the assigned SAP modules for the business function
•	Train key users
•	Create and maintain documentation and ensures its actuality
•	Alignment with counterparts in other sites, by ensuring their involvement in changes, update of documentation.
•	Can take roles within the CCC processes (e.g. Patch Manager, Transport Manager) or a coordinator within the associated modules for the Patch & Exchange Day
•	Ensures / verify that the implementation of business processes is compliant to the global template
•	Can take over responsibilities as technical leader, project or subproject leader
Job Requirements:
•	Bachelor’s Degree in Computer Science or Information Technology or equivalent qualification.
•	Minimum 5 years of SAP hands-on experience. SD core, second module WM or MM
•	Minimum 2 full cycle implementation experience in manufacturing environment
•	Must be able to speak Mandarin to communicate with internal Chinese counterparts
•	Self-starter with high initiative, pro-active, independent and team player, good problem solving and project management skills
•	Willing to travel
Please can all interested candidates forward a copy of there up to date CV to michelle.hoangcv@amoriabond.com.sg
for immediate interview.
Amoria Bond operates as an employment agency and employment business. No terminology in this advert is intended to discriminate on the grounds of age, and we confirm that we are happy to accept applications from persons of any age for this role.
